summary: An ordinance relating to Seattle Toll Bridge Franchise granted by Ordinance No. 58910, providing new effective dates for the commencement and termination thereof, and the commencement of constitution of the Toll Bridge thereby contemplated, correcting the description of the center line of the westerly terminal of said bridge, providing for the acceptance of such amendments, and amending Sections 1, 3 and 5, of Ordinance No. 58910.
